data.description: This is a gorgeous home with many upgrades including Granite counter tops and Engineered Laminate flooring.The 2563 sq ft floor plan means lots of room with 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths. there's plenty of room for any size family. The 3 car garage offers plenty of space.The glass slider opens up to a spacious backyard. Front and back yards have automatic sprinklers for ease of care. The stucco exterior and tile roof mean years of low maintenance. Only 15 mins to USA Parkway and two minutes to shopping. Come take a look.
